Add README file for RETE II Knowledge-Based System

This commit introduces a comprehensive README file for the RETE II 
knowledge-based system implemented in Ruby. The documentation includes 
a detailed overview of the core features, such as the RETE II engine, 
domain-specific language for rule definition, and the blackboard memory 
system. Additionally, it provides instructions for basic usage, usage of 
the DSL, and examples of the stock trading expert system.

This addition aims to enhance user understanding and facilitate 
onboarding by providing essential setup and usage guidance.